author: Kara
title: Spiderman 5th Birthday Party
text:
Swing in for this Spiderman 5th Birthday Party by Chella Levesque of
Chella Levesque Inc., out of Vancouver, BC CANADA!
Filled to the brim with the most amazing Spiderman-inspired decor and deets, this spidey event will have you crawling with fun!
Favorite details, include:
- Awesome Spiderman Themed Panel Backdrop
- Spiderman-inspire Balloon Garlands
- Superhero + Cityscape Pedestal Dessert Tables
- Custom Spiderman Partyware
- Spiderman Cookies
- Ghost Chairs adorned with Superhero Expressions
Spiderman 5th Birthday Party
Party Details:
“This family has been a long time client of mine and has the most stunning home in West Vancouver Canada. Like all little boys, he loves SPIDERMAN. In fact, the cake had to be red velvet because that is what Spiderman would eat. Client gave me her theme and we brought it to life in the most extraordinary way.” – Chella | Chella Levesque Inc.

Event Producer: Chella Levesque Inc.
